{
  "texts": [
    "We conduct extensive experiments to validate the effectiveness of RIFL.",
    "Our results show that RIFL significantly improves the instruction-following capabilities of Llama 4 Maverick on various challenging benchmarks.",
    "Specifically, RIFL achieves a 6.7% absolute improvement on our newly proposed AdvancedIF benchmark, and also shows strong performance on public benchmarks like MultiChallenge and IFEval.",
    "Our ablation studies confirm the superiority of our finetuned rubric verifier over vanilla LLM judges and demonstrate the effectiveness of our reward design and shaping.",
    "These strong empirical results highlight the efficacy of our proposed RIFL pipeline, showing the promise of rubric-based RL for both training and evaluation of advanced instruction-following capabilities of LLMs."
  ]
}